@startuml
title Statechart diagram of Plane Lifecycle

[*] --> Order
state Order
state Arrival
state Preparation
state Operations
state Maintenance
state OutOfService
state Removed

Order --> Arrival : plane arrives
Arrival --> Preparation : prepare plane
Preparation --> Operations : assign to operations based on condition and schedule
Operations --> Maintenance : no more scheduled flights or maintenance required
Maintenance --> Preparation : checked and serviced
Preparation --> OutOfService : take out of service if not available for use
OutOfService --> Removed : permanently withdrawn from service
@enduml
